Text:
Thanks, but this torrent is royally screwed up.

There's 4 zip files, and opening them yields HomeInventory.part1.rar, HomeInventory.part2.rar, HomeInventory.part3.rar, and, you guessed it - HomeInventory.part4.rar. Opening the rars gets nothing but empty folders.

THERE IS NO APP INCLUDED! There IS a keygen, but NO APP.
